o called Irene Pool, is a gorgeous natural pool and one of Pachmarhi's less-visited destinations. Despite all the movement, it is easy to see the pool's bottom, and the water doesn't reach higher than the waist in most areas. It's the ideal location for some leisurely time spent in the cold sea. Visitors must first walk for about 10 minutes on flat land to get here, and then you must climb a steep path for 300 meters. The greatest time to view this gorgeous mountain pool is during or right after the rainy season. Honeycomb remnants, vibrant butterflies, and the verdant Satpura Hills surroundings may all be seen all around the route. 6 kilometres from the Pachmarhi Bus Stand. Times: 8 AM to 6 PM. Next TopicTourist Places in Kanchipuram ? prev next ? For Videos Join Our Youtube Channel: Join Now Feedback Send your Feedback to [email protected] Help Others, Please Share Learn Latest Tutorials Splunk SPSS Swagger Transact-SQL Tumblr ReactJS Regex Reinforcement Learning R Programming RxJS React Native Python Design Patterns Python Pillow Python Turtle Keras Preparation Aptitude Reasoning Verbal Ability Interview Questions Company Questions Trending Technologies Artificial Intelligence AWS Selenium Cloud Computing Hadoop ReactJS Data Science Angular 7 Blockchain Git Machine Learning DevOps B.Tech / MCA DBMS Data Structures DAA Operating System Computer Network Compiler Design Computer Organization Discrete Mathematics Ethical Hacking Computer Graphics Software Engineering Web Technology Cyber Security Automata C Programming C++ Java .Net Python Programs Control System Data Mining Data Warehouse Javatpoint Services JavaTpoint offers too many high quality services. Mail us on [email protected], to get more information about given services. Website Designing Website Development Java Development PHP Development WordPress Graphic Designing Logo Digital Marketing On Page and Off Page SEO PPC Content Development Corporate Training Classroom and Online Training Data Entry Trainin